**Day Trade:** So, I mostly focus on day trading, in this channel you will be finding daily updates about the information that Bitcoin, is generating. Starting off by our FIRST point of vision which is going to be about

-Daily Value
-Daily Initial Balance

-Previous US Session High

**Swing Trade:**
This one will be based on a lot of strategies, it depends on the coin that I will be trading, if it's an altcoin / classical coin. Just like on day trading, whenever I provide a Swing Trade I will try my best to explain my point of vision to you.
Here you won't only be updated about the market only, but you will also learn with us. We will try our best to provide you useful knowledge. Be active, supportive, and stay loyal to our community. AND LETS MOON! üåîüöÄ

The Core PCE price index is a measure of the change in the cost of goods and services purchased by consumers, excluding food and energy. It is distinct from the Core CPI in that it only considers items that individuals buy and consume, with prices weighted according to overall spending per item. This provides valuable insights into consumer spending behavior.

The expected value for this release is 0.4%, while the previous figure was 0.6%. The Core PCE Price Index is a critical metric for the Federal Reserve to assess inflation, and they monitor it closely to inform their future monetary policy decisions. A weaker-than-anticipated outcome would be favorable for risk assets such as cryptocurrencies.
